column2: SELECT   p.objid, p.petromag_r - p.extinction_r as magPetro_r, p.petromag_g - p.extinction_g as magPetro_g,   p.fiberMag_r, p.petroMag_r, p.modelMag_r,   p.fiberMag_z, p.petroMag_z, p.modelMag_z,    s.veldisp as sigma    INTO   myDB.cgs_out    FROM   myDB.cgs as m, PhotoObj as p, specObj, as s    WHERE   p.objid = m.objid AND   p.objID = s.bestObjID
